<p>Trace-I generally agree with your assessment of the book. Indeed, I didn&#8217;t finish reading it for the reasons you articulate. The book was an accompaniment to a BBC special series, and that explains some of its flaws.<br />
Lately, Ferguson seems to have changed his tune a bit, becoming more critical of the debt based system. Yes, even Oxford trained scholars can grow.-Dominick</p>
